* 1944: Lieutenant Commander ($74,105)
* 1951: Commander ($86,827)
* 1956: Captain ($106,908)
* 1958: Rear Admiral Lower Half ($126,920)
* 1960: Rear Admiral ($149,534)
* 1961: Vice Admiral ($180,536)
* 1965: Admiral ($187,959)

